      <odd id="aspace_ea6642bd3cf3be970511eefbd559eadc">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 37 (YRG 37), Records of associations, institutes, centers, and organizations affiliated with Yale University.</p>  
