      <altformavail id="aspace_fa6eca84646caa544d333bbfe035af5b">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>The entire collection is also available on microfilm (442 frames on 1 reel, 35mm.) from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no. HM170.</p>  
      </altformavail>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_30e32bf928261322ac87f927c64523b6">
